metadata.name: Dissociation agent
metadata.description:
Special service of internal communication shut down. Wave of unconsciusness slowly encounters your inner self. You don't know nothing anymore, but feel everything.  
There are no names, no differences and no boundaries. 
Inch by inch, memory and experience fade, leaving only black nothingless.  
Inch by inch, memory and experience fade, black nothingless black nothingless.  
Inch by inch, memory and black nothingless, black nothingless black nothingless.  
Inch by inch, black nothingless black nothingless, black nothingless black nothingless.  
Black nothingless, black nothingless black nothingless, black nothingless black nothingless.
